-- Poland to offer bonds due January, July 2019 at Thursday switch
-- By Wiktor Szary
-- Tue Sep 16, 2014 09:04AM EDT
-- None



WARSAW, Sept 16 (Reuters) - Poland will offer bonds due January 2019 and July 2019 at a switch tender on Thursday, the finance ministry said in a statement on Tuesday.

The ministry added that it would sell the bonds in exchange for papers due January 2015 and April 2015.